  <brief_title>Non-bridging Fixator Versus Percutaneous Pinning for Distal Radius Fractures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Non-bridging Radio-radial Fixator Compared to Percutaneous Pinning for Unstable Distal Radius Fracture. A Prospective Randomized Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Hopital de l'Enfant-Jesus</agency>
